Two points. Technically we were not outnumbered in 2016, we were outmaneuvered.



More importantly, there is no finish line. Speaking as one who is not young, you keeping running, keep fighting, on and on and on. Year after year, election after election, issue after issue, generation after generation. This is how we make the world better. Do it.
